name: City & Regional Fuels
description: City & Regional Fuels, founded by Bruce & Sue Kilpatrick in 1985 to distribute BP products throughout the South Western corner of Western Australia, has grown to become one of the leading fuel distributors in this diverse and productive area. The Company has a strong commitment to Health, Safety, Security and the Environment. Quality Control Endorsement together with our involvement in the Landcare Project & community and support groups lend the basis for the way we do business. The team at City & Regional pride ourselves on our professional and personal customer service and by using the latest technologies and supplying the highest quality in fuel and lubricant products, we take the stress out of supply in the South West. The City & Regional Distributor card is another initiative aimed at making life easier for our customers. With retail sites strategically located throughout our trading area and informative detailed reporting we can make your record keeping a breeze. By providing products and services of the highest quality in a prompt and efficient manner and at a fair price, City & Regional aims to enhance its position as a leading fuel distributor in the South West.
